'''Louis Mellis''' is a Scottish voice actor, who provided the voice of [[Darth Sion]] in the video game ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''.

Louis also works as a scriptwriter, having co-written the feature film [[Wikipedia:Sexy Beast|''Sexy Beast'']], and currently can be heard in the United Kingdom on [[Wikipedia:BBC Radio 1|BBC Radio 1]] as a one of the main imaging voiceover talents.

